items.value: This sketchy teen is the school's delivery boy! He may offload his work, but he takes the job very seriously...
Just throw it at them, they'll pick it up.
Hey have you delivered that item yet?
You did? Good. Now take these points as payment.
You didn't? Well... it looks like you're going to be paying the price...
You lost it?! Well... it looks like you're going to be paying the price...
Not yet? You better have it delivered by the next time I see you...
I hope you didn't need those! Because I'll be taking them as tax!
You can keep the item you STOLE from me... but I'll be taking the rest as tax.
